Asigmatic

431 awarded this award in 1398 challenges.

This award celebrates high voter variance, that is, images which have split the crowd. The award was originally suggested by another user, and can be read about here. As opposed to many other awards, this is deterministic and is awarded to the user that received the highest vote variance amongst the submissions.
